    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[四年磨一剑，腾讯云亮出业内首款全自研AIGC存储解决方案]]></title>
        <id>2247549135_1</id>
        <link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg4Mjc2MjQyMQ==&amp;mid=2247549135&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=7afccf96edc9df663ab8337b2ffa8930&amp;chksm=cf53f715f8247e038bfe2f3fb20b24bb8eaac296f34577fae71c1a04314e9e18f95e4b9618b9#rd"/>
        <updated>2024-04-16T16:08:02.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;" data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><img class="rich_pages __bg_gif wxw-img" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="578" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="72" data-imgfileid="100303898" data-ratio="0.125" data-s="300,640" data-type="gif" data-w="640" style="width: 578px;visibility: visible !important;height: 72px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/Pn4Sm0RsAujqPrtpN5QqqOuSG0AdUUx8wRg3vvr7aQJicdC0cHDBqZrJBZajQUXx97BwNaAE6L6x7OGlsTIpWjw/640?wx_fmt=gif"></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">大模型时代汹涌而至，可谓势不可挡，引领着行业变革的浪潮。今年4月，艾瑞咨询在《AIGC系列报告——中国AIGC产业全景报告》预测，到2028年，中国AIGC产业规模预计将达到7202亿元，中国AIGC产业生态日益稳固，完成重点领域、关键场景的技术价值兑现，逐步建立完善模型即服务产业生态。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">此背景下，数据浪潮的翻涌和模型复杂度的不断攀升，驱动着AI基础设施的变革。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">早前，腾讯云曾针对AIGC场景，推出了基于星脉网络的大模型训练集群HCC、向量数据库以及行业大模型服务MaaS等一系列全链路服务。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">这次轮到了存储。上周，腾讯云宣布云存储解决方案面向AIGC场景全面升级，<strong>针对AI大模型数据采集清洗、训练、推理、数据治理全流程</strong>，提供更加高效、可靠的存储解决之道。据悉，这是业内目前首款实现存储引擎全面自研的云存储解决方案。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100138475" data-ratio="0.562037037037037" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Pn4Sm0RsAuhUfW7nV3YUpuYrHOsl8qia11lYPfJGcWft7NYUfT9WqHW7e7Vlgd4A46ZADWbFwBe0zxDcpaTkkNg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><br></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: center;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="93" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="33" data-imgfileid="100303903" data-ratio="0.8" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="120" style="height: 74px;font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;width: 93px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Pn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06QFVIXibMwPPd6fqj78HsRjJ5S4jPGWUnrbo52KPZ4jhib7y5e0bybRibQg/640?wx_fmt=png"></p><h3 style="margin: 0pt 8px 24px;break-after: avoid;text-align: center;font-family: 等线;color: rgb(26, 26, 26);font-weight: bold;font-size: 14pt;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;"><strong>各方面技术升级，自研存储优势凸显</strong></span></h3><p style="text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong><br></strong></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">随大模型的持续演进，传统存储无法满足大模型的研发流程，旧概念已然被颠覆，高效存储数据已成为“模型精炼”不可或缺的一环。新趋势下，腾讯云针对AIGC场景推出的云存储解决方案，对AI大模型的研发和生产流程提供了高效、全面的支撑。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">正如腾讯云存储总经理马文霜所说的：“2021年的时候，腾讯云存储产品的性能就领先业界。今天，我们针对AIGC等新型场景进行性能和功能的全面升级。”</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">具体来说，本次方案对AIGC的价值体现在这几个方面：</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">在数据采集上，腾讯云自研的百EB级存储引擎YottaStore支撑对象存储COS的卓越性能。YottaStore的研发，成为腾讯云在超大规模数据存储领域取得的重要突破，除了具备超高速公网访问能力，还能实现海量弹性存储规模，为AI大模型的数据收集与清洗提供强有力的支持。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">进入数据清洗环节，腾讯云以数据加速器GooseFS，提升数据访问性能，实现了高达数TBps的惊人读取带宽。这一技术突破不仅为计算任务的高速运行提供了有力支撑，更大幅提升了数据清洗的整体效率，确保了数据处理流程的顺畅与高效。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 1px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">在数据训练上，腾讯云自研了业内唯一的云原生并行文件存储系统——CFS Turbo，它基于自研的分布式高性能存储引擎Histor，通过减少数据拷贝和虚拟化消耗，以及应用侧的自研并行文件传输协议，实现了高性能的存储和访问。此外，CFS Turbo也针对AIGC的多种场景进行优化，提升读写性能，如今已被广泛应用于AI人工智能、高性能计算、自动驾驶、工业仿真和影视特效等多个领域。</span></p><p style="text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100303908" data-ratio="0.6584440227703985" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1054" style="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/q7kM1wTg0ej9QP66s0s4d9deEP7UVOzUtLvGNwVCa2FVvX7TdoYZXueVkkIGk0gEnBaEMsbEg16VD8hOXc0LKA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><br></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: center;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="92" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="33" data-imgfileid="100303902" data-ratio="0.8" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="120" style="height: 74px;font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;width: 92px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Pn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06QRNnF4oqkNO3sG9icI4NRlsXZaMRDzf6ohtF4jBaKRqKkqAds9uiaC32A/640?wx_fmt=png"></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: center;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;"><strong style="color: rgb(26, 26, 26);font-family: 等线;font-size: 14pt;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: left;">数据审核得到优化，为内容生产注入活力</strong></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong style="color: rgb(26, 26, 26);font-family: 等线;font-size: 14pt;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: left;"><br></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 15px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: center;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><br></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">除了重视数据采集、数据清洗和训练环节，人工智能技术的广泛应用，也让更多企业机构意识到：内容的安全与合规在大模型时代也变得愈发重要。据Gartner预测，到2025年，70%的企业机构将把如何可持续、道德地使用AI列为其首要关注的问题。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">为了让内容的安全与合规得到保障，给内容生产链路注入活力，存储的“护航工作”指向数据审核。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">这一环节中，有数据万象CI高效的审核机制，迅速对上传的媒体内容进行精确筛选，确保不符合规范的内容被及时过滤，从而维护平台的纯净与秩序。此外，为了进一步增强AI作品的安全性和可追踪性，数据万象CI特别引入了图片隐式水印功能，为每个AI作品生成一个独一无二的专属ID，能被精确地识别和追踪。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">随后，为了满足现代数据处理需求，一站式智能数据处理、分析与检索解决方案MetaInsight应运而生，通过AI技术的融入，赋予了存储系统更强大、快速的多模态检索能力。据了解，MetaInsight不仅关注数据的存储，更着眼于如何释放数据的潜在价值，使其能够为客户和用户提供真正的帮助。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><br></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: center;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="90" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="33" data-imgfileid="100303897" data-ratio="0.8" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="120" style="height: 72px;font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;width: 90px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Pn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06Ql2XfgrkmMOvk8s9px34c0xJDYyGJC1Edr4fRs5fYiaxhEJGWadUv8jA/640?wx_fmt=png"></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: center;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;"><strong style="color: rgb(26, 26, 26);font-family: 等线;font-size: 14pt;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: left;">80%头部大模型企业之选</strong></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><br></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">数据存储需求的爆发式增长，除了为大模型企业带来了新机遇、新价值，也让它们对数据存储与处理方案的高效性、稳定性及安全性要求愈发严苛。毕竟研发中涉及的数据收集与清洗、模型训练以及推理等环节，每一个都不可或缺。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">数据显示，腾讯云AIGC存储方案凭借其高效、稳定、安全的特点，帮助企业进行前瞻性布局。目前已获得80%头部大模型企业的青睐，并取得显著成效。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">在实际应用层面，MiniMax这家新兴的AI模型公司通过使用腾讯云对象存储COS及智能数据处理平台数据万象，有效地处理和分析了大规模的AIGC内容。腾讯云提供的快速安全审核服务，保障了MiniMax业务的规范运作和稳定性，审核速度达到了百毫秒级别。同时，腾讯云的数据预处理功能也提高了MiniMax的数据流转效率，使其能够更加专注于核心业务的开发和市场推广。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">除此之外，百川智能也通过采用该方案而受益。通过引入腾讯云的高性能分布式缓存GooseFS和高性能并行文件存储CFS Turbo，实现了显著提升的IOPS和吞吐量，这在技术上是一个显著的进步。这些技术应用使得百川智能可以高效地执行模型训练的checkpoint读写操作，进而提升了GPU的使用效率和作业处理速度。这些进步不仅为百川智能在业务测带来了实质性的益处，也为其在AI领域的发展奠定了较为坚实的基础。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">腾讯云存储总经理陈峥告诉CSDN：“我认为，产品是市场竞争力的核心。我们提前布局了详尽的解决方案，并在细节上精心打磨。因此在AIGC行业蓬勃发展时期，得以抓住了机遇。”</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 15px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><br></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: center;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;"><strong><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-cropselx1="0" data-cropselx2="96" data-cropsely1="0" data-cropsely2="33" data-imgfileid="100303895" data-ratio="0.8" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="120" style="height: 77px;font-family: -apple-system-font, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;width: 96px;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/Pn4Sm0RsAujX5kS5KQ6BaBUsy1RqR06QH4pfFF4icsdP5pedH9O9rrymeKBk50zNDSWYeqXmpEXwB0gK32DrhTQ/640?wx_fmt=png"></strong></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: center;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;"><strong style="color: rgb(26, 26, 26);font-family: 等线;font-size: 14pt;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: left;">四年布局自研，旨在自主可控</strong></span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-align: justify;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong style="color: rgb(26, 26, 26);font-family: 等线;font-size: 14pt;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: left;"><br></strong></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 15px;text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;"><br></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">本次发布的AIGC存储解决方案，早在四、五年前已经开始研发。不过，彼时AIGC还没有成为潮流，市场上面对高性能存储的需求并不旺盛，但腾讯云为何那时就决定全情投入？</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">答案一方面是对市场需求的预见，另一方面是对自研可控的坚持。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">腾讯云存储总经理马文霜在接受CSDN采访时透露：“在2019-2021年，我们已经洞察到高性能存储领域未来的巨大需求和潜力。当时，传统AI应用、高性能计算及自动驾驶等领域，已经对存储技术要求极高，无论是存储带宽、文件操作的IOPS还是其他方面，都展现出了明显的增长趋势，这些实际应用场景代表了未来发展高性能存储大有可为。”</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">彼时，采用现成的非自研的通用方案，是云厂商的普遍做法，也基本能够满足用户对高性能文件存储的需求，但在面对市场快速变化时，原厂的支持未必能及时到位，因此有时难以满足用户日益迫切的需求。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">除了洞察市场需求，优先自研的传统一直是腾讯云的“选择”，力求实现技术的自主可控。早在2021年第四季度，腾讯云就主动进行了收入结构的调整，明确将“健康可持续”作为To B业务的增长目标，多项举措中包括提升自研产品的竞争力、推动产品集成以及丰富合作伙伴生态。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">技术的可控代表着产品可控，面临不可预测的挑战时，服务能跟得上、做得好。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100303909" data-ratio="0.5115384615384615" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="1040" style="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/q7kM1wTg0ej9QP66s0s4d9deEP7UVOzUfFbTh8yko0c0picKJodDnch6liaa8wR7cEotbHF7vDiawDAk6PUwopfNw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg"></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">针对自研的“可控性”，腾讯云存储总经理陈峥坦言这对于腾讯云来说具有重要意义，他表示：“我们最为看重的是产品的可控性，即确保在整个产品生命周期中，我们始终掌握着产品的发展方向和核心技术，确保其始终符合我们的战略目标和市场需求。”</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">为此，腾讯云投入大量的人力资源进行研发，在当时满足自动驾驶、AI等领域对高性能存储的迫切需求，也为未来的市场竞争奠定基础。如今，面临突如其来的AIGC浪潮，厚积薄发的腾讯云存储在成功接住客户需求的同时，也对方案进行了多方面迭代。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">一直以来，存储与算力、网络构成“数据中心三大件”，为大模型的生产提供稳固的数据基石，确保大模型中的信息能够迅速、流畅地进行读写操作。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">随着大模型行业逐渐从“百模大战”走向多模态时代，多模态技术在不同场景下的应用日益广泛，这对未来的腾讯云存储来说是一次新考验。面对客户需求的多样化和技术迭代的加速，仍然存在诸多的机遇与调整，腾讯云将如何调整和优化解决方案，以适应这一时代的变革，我们拭目以待。</span></p><p class="js_darkmode__130" style="outline: 0px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: normal;"><span style="outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong style="outline: 0px;caret-color: rgb(123, 127, 131);color: rgb(121, 123, 170);font-family: -apple-system, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimHei, sans-serif;font-size: 14.6667px;text-align: start;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100065470" data-ratio="0.10277777777777777" data-w="1080" style="outline: 0px;visibility: visible !important;width: 660.958px !important;" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/oZsJseC8PzWbahZOLT9mlZvZDhD69hOLWTkPicrxDcwPQmic5xGMZSfAjqgfGagw9C7gW8DjHAUVeARsyL1ia9F3A/640?wx_fmt